Duppy is a command line tool to recurse multiple directories and find duplicate files. It then provides an interactive menu to act on these duplicates.

python dup.py dir1 dir2 ...

Available commands in interactive menu:-
- list - list all directories with duplicate files, numbered
- #num - list all duplicate files in selected directory numbered in original list command

- open #num1 #num2 ... - open directories in GUI window
- move #num1 #num2 ... - move duplicates to dup_backup directory in CWD
- dups #num1 #num2 ... - show all duplicates in specified directories
- nondups #num1 #num2 ... - show all non-duplicates in specified directories

- filter - list all active filters
- filter <string> - filter all directories containing <string> from list command

- quit - exit program
- reload - rescan directories
- clear - clear the screen